OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy cloud
OL,6,Fwith further showers into the evening
OL,7,Fand overnight. A fresh northwesterly
OL,8,Fbreeze will continue. Temperatures
OL,9,Ffalling to low single figures but
OL,10,Fremaining generally frost free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother day of bright spells
OL,13,Fand occasional heavy showers, these
OL,14,Fcontinuing to bring the risk of some
OL,15,Fhail and thunder. Turning generally
OL,16,Fdrier through the evening.
OL,17,FTemperatures remaining cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
